{
  "id": "adv_card_mku_01_01",
  "title": "初音ミク 1話 教えて、マネージャーさん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――マジカルミライ10th Anniversary",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Magical Mirai 10th Anniversary",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "in VENUS STAGE",
      "translations": {
        "en": "in VENUS STAGE",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本イベントにトリエル出演が決まった数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A few days after TRINITYAiLE was\nselected to perform at this event",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、ミクの呼び出し方は……\nこれで良かったかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ if I want to call Miku…\nIs this how I do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1993.1654612000002,
          "startTime": 14.6264987945
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku001.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは、{user}さん\nどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ {user}-san.\nWhat's up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7606742859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ミク、いきなり呼び出してすまない\nトリエルのみんなが作詞に苦戦してるみたいなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miku‚ sorry for calling you out of the blue.\nIt seems that everyone from TRINITYAiLE is struggling with the lyrics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.0606742859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "初めての試みだから無理もないが……\nそれで、ミクに相談出来ないかなと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's their first attempt‚ so it's understandable…\nSo‚ I thought maybe I can ask some advice from you‚ Miku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8606742859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん！　私も作詞の経験はないけど……\n協力出来ることがあるなら頑張るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! I don't have experience with lyrics‚ but…\nI'll do my best if there's anything I can do to help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、何か言葉を掛けるなら……\n私はもっといろいろと知らないといけないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if you want me to have a conversatoin with them…\nI need to know more about various things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku004.m4a",
      "text": "私はバーチャルの世界にいるから\nデータベースで公式情報を調べることが出来るけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I exist in the virtual world‚\nso I can look up official information in the database…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5940076192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku005.m4a",
      "text": "もっと深いこと――トリエルのみんなが\nどんな人なのかを私は知らないなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don't know deeper things—like what kind of people\neveryone from TRINITYAiLE is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、{user}さんにいろいろと\n教えてほしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I want you to tell me various things‚\n{user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、それもそうか\n分かった、俺が知ってる限りのことを教えるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ that makes sense.\nUnderstood‚ I'll tell you everything I know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.7273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。あ、そうだ\n場所を移動してもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. Oh‚ by the way‚\nCan we change the location?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.7273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　それは……どうして？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Why is that…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.0273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku008.m4a",
      "text": "私はまだ、事務所しか見てないから\nこの街の景色をもっと見てみたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've only seen the office so far‚\nI want to see more of this town's scenery.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、分かった\n場所を選ぶ必要はあるけど、大丈夫だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I see.\nWe'll need to choose a place‚ but it's fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9606742859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku009.m4a",
      "text": "どうして、場所を選ぶ必要があるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do we need to choose a place?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "君のファンは沢山いるから\n驚かせてしまうと思うんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because you have many fans.\nI think it would surprise them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku010.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なの？\nそれが本当なら、嬉しいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so?\nIf that's true‚ I'm happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0606742859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku011.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、場所は{user}さんに\nお任せするね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚\nI'll leave the choice of location to you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5940076192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.2273409526
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.2273409526
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "よし、今はほとんど人がいないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ there aren't many people here now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2940076192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.3606742859
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku012.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……素敵な眺め。辺りで鳥が鳴いてて\n賑やかな街の音が遠くに聞こえる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… what a lovely view. I can hear birds singing nearby.\nI can faintly hear the lively sounds of the city in the distance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.8606742859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.0940076192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "気に入ってくれて良かった。それでトリエルのことだが\nまず、天動さんは真面目でストイックなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad you like it. Now‚ about TRINITYAiLE…\nFirst‚ Tendou-san is serious and dedicated.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0940076192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "でも時々抜けていることもあって\nそういう面も含めてファンに愛されてるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But sometimes‚ she can be a bit absent-minded.\nIncluding that aspect‚ She is loved by the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4940076192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.8273409526
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku013.m4a",
      "text": "素敵な子なんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She sounds wonderful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.0940076192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "次は鈴村さんだな。彼女はおっとりしていて落ち着きが\nある。それにライブMCの面白さにも定評があるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next is Suzumura-san. She's calm and composed.\nShe's also known for her entertaining MC skills during live performances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.3940076192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "あと方言……京都弁が特徴的だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And she has a distinctive dialect… Kyoto dialect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.5273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.4940076192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_01-mku014.m4a",
      "text": "少ししか聞いてないけど、優雅なメロディーみたいで\nとっても素敵な話し方だったよ。もっと聞いてみたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've only heard a little bit of it‚ but it sounded like an elegant melody.\nI'd love to hear more of it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.1273409526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
